These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea, orchid, aconite, balloon-flower
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, rowing, water-polo, parkour
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Flower   | azalea | orchid | marigold | balloon-flower | aconite |
| Sport   | parkour    | climbing | rowing     | water-polo       | swimming  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different pets are kept: ferret, horse, bird, pony, goat
House: wooden, cape-cod, craftsman, ranch-style, modern
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
5. the owner of the horse is the craftsman house##1
6. the modern house is the owner of the goat##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Pet      | horse | bird | ferret | pony | goat |
| House   | craftsman  | ranch-style   | wooden       | cape-cod    | modern   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, camping, drawing, dancing
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, water-polo, handball, snowboarding, sailing
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby        | camping | drawing | puzzles | card-games | dancing |
| Sport   | water-polo  | skateboarding      | sailing | handball | snowboarding      |

