.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
5 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, dog, fish, rabbit
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: marigold, sunflower, poppy, bellflower, balloon-flower
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Pet   | fish    | ferret        | dog | guinea-pig | rabbit |
| Flower     | marigold | bellflower | balloon-flower  | sunflower   | poppy |

