.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
House: farmhouse, craftsman, cape-cod, palace, art-deco
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, trance, gospel, folk, soul
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
2. the fan of trance is the art-deco house##1
3. the fan of gospel is on the left of the palace house##1
4. the fan of gospel is in the middle##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
6. the fan of soul is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| House    | cape-cod   | farmhouse     | craftsman   | palace         | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | disco | folk | gospel | soul | trance     |

