.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
City: boston, venice, colone, berlin, san-francisco
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, american, polish, indian
1. the polish is in the middle##1
2. the pakistani is on the far right##1
3. the american is on the left of the polish##1
4. the american is the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
6. the indian is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| City       | berlin   | colone   | venice | san-francisco | boston |
| Nationality   | dutch | american | polish   | indian | pakistani       |

