.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
House: cottage, victorian, cape-cod, art-deco, wooden
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat, ritmeester, dunhill, alhambra
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is the cottage house##1
3. the wooden house is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| House     | victorian   | cape-cod  | wooden      | cottage | art-deco     |
| Cigar   | dunhill | ritmeester | baccarat | fonseca   | alhambra |

