.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, mirinda, 7up, soy-milk
City: hannover, marseilles, hamburg, new-york, london
1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
6. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage     | iced-tea | lemonade       | soy-milk | 7up | mirinda    |
| City   | new-york   | london | hamburg  | marseilles     | hannover |

