.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  journalist, architect, analyst, engineer, mechanic
5 different games are played: snooker, go, mah-jongg, poker, chess
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the analyst is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the architect is on the far right##1
4. the engineer is on the far left##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing go##1
6. the mechanic is the person playing go##1
7. the engineer is on the left of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Job         | engineer | journalist | analyst | mechanic | architect |
| Game   | mah-jongg       | poker   | chess         | go   | snooker   |

