.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, writer, designer, bartender, engineer
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, airplane, train, jet-ski, bus
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the writer##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the designer##1
3. the person driving the train is the freelancer##1
4. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Job   | engineer | bartender | writer | designer | freelancer |
| Transport           | bus      | airplane    | jet-ski  | car     | train     |

