.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, pilot, electrician, architect, accountant
5 different games are played: canasta, chess, whist, scrabble, snooker
1. the electrician is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person playing chess is the architect##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
4. the mechanic is on the right of the person playing chess##1
5. the accountant is on the far right##1
6. the accountant is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
7. the person playing snooker is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Job   | architect | mechanic  | electrician | pilot | accountant |
| Game    | chess    | scrabble | snooker   | canasta       | whist        |

