.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, december, november, may, september
House: modern, cape-cod, ranch-style, colonial, tower
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is the tower house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the ranch-style house is on the left of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Birthday    | june | may          | november    | september | december  |
| House   | ranch-style  | tower | modern | colonial | cape-cod |

