.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: pink, azure, chestnut, lavender, purple
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, july, december, august, april
1. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who likes purple is the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Color   | chestnut | pink      | lavender | azure | purple |
| Birthday     | august  | july | march     | april     | december  |

