.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, orchid, balloon-flower, tulip, azalea
There 5 different types of food: grapes, spinach, plum, mango, potato
1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person eating potato##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Flower      | azalea | balloon-flower | begonia      | tulip | orchid      |
| Food   | spinach  | mango       | grapes | potato  | plum |

