.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-15::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, horse, cat, turtle, hamster
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, game, old-henry, tiparillo, siglo
1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is the owner of the cat##1
5. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
6. the game-smoker is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
7. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
| Pet           | turtle     | hamster | bird | cat  | horse |
| Cigar   | chaman | siglo               | game     | old-henry | tiparillo |

