3. the person playing billiard is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the cat is the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the rat is the person playing go##1
7. the owner of the snake is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |  3   |    4    |   5    |
| Pet   | cat   | frog    | mouse | rat   | snake |
| Game     | scrabble | billiard | monopoly | go | snooker    |

