There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, orange, coral, lavender
1. the person who likes coral is in the middle##1
2. the cain-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who likes lavender##1
5. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
6. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Cigar   | aristoff   | siglo  | cain | tiparillo | prince  |
| Color         | aquamarine | orange | coral  | lavender    | purple |

