.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  social-worker, lawyer, pilot, librarian, project-manager
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: july, september, february, may, april
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the pilot##1
2. the librarian is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is the librarian##1
5. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the lawyer is on the left of the librarian##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Job   | project-manager     | pilot       | social-worker     | lawyer  | librarian  |
| Birthday      | may | july | september | april | february |

