.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: video-games, skydiving, board-games, gardening, woodworking
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, yellow, ivory, azure, blood-red
1. the person who likes yellow is in the middle##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | woodworking | board-games | video-games | gardening |
| Color           | blood-red | azure  | yellow    | ebony  | ivory   |

 